window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From the Audible Originals anthology <i>Birds of Prey: The Harlan Coben Challenge</i> comes this thrilling story of deceit and duplicity by <i>New York Times</i> best seller C.J. Box.</p> <p>It starts with a stranger walking into a campsite, seemingly out of nowhere. It ends with that same stranger at the Denver airport. Along the way, he has acquired a prize that will be his salvation.</p> <p>But the road to Easy Street can take unexpected turns. And the only certainty about a sure thing is that nothing is certain at all.</p> <p>Watch for <i>Birds of Prey: The Harlan Coben Challenge</i>, coming to Audible on Oct. 6, 2022.</p> <p><i>Birds of Prey</i> was created in partnership with International Thriller Writers (ITW).</p>"; 
